Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, man!\N It's {\i1}my{\i0} turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Buster Blader!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice move!\N Get 'im! Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Sign"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really want to see this\N town again before I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is the town\N my brother and the guys fought\N really hard in during Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see\N this town properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks just like Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi began the search\N for his memory on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right in this same spot,\N after seeing this stone slab,\N it all began...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ancient Egyptian king carved here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt in my mind that this person is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is there a carving of Yugi on that stone tablet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Puzzle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu, I have just realized who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The soul of an Ancient Egyptian king who was trapped inside the Millennium Puzzle for thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}That{\b1} is who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be? Does Yugi's other soul really live inside of the Millennium Puzzle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all this time, it's no wonder I've forgotten everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am Ishizu Ishtar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For 3000 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have protected a piece of the Pharaoh's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's... a Millennium Item!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is also where we met\N Ishizu-{\i0}san{\i1} for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ishizu-{\i0}san{\i1}\N told us about the existence\N of another Millennium Item...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, one {\b0}other{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person standing beside Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The resemblance is too great. Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The carving on this stone slab...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,predicted our present-day battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the only way I can find the answers to find my lost memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That palette... surprised me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was {\i1}shocked{\i0} when\N I saw it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the spot Jounouchi had\N his first Duel of Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi! Ya better give up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's Esper Roba. A Duelist who has super powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right! He read every one a' my strategies with his super powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ya can't win against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know a thing about his "super powers", but I'm gonna fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ya dumbass! Don't do it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cheering for him\N in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see it myself,\N but Honda-{\i1}san{\i0} guided me through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm! That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see Jounouchi's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't miss the moment of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Honda-{\i0}san{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, you don't need to comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The nurse told me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother is losing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, I didn't want you \Nto get you worried, Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother is playing hard.\NI want to support him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am bound to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless to struggle more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just surrender now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1} is watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honda called, they are watching your duel through the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honda and Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1} are cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honda...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must work hard, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Domino Port, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no {\i1}way{\i0} I could\N ever forget what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bomb set up atop this container.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Try anything and I'll press this switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}dropping the container right on top of that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, you get to go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...knowing one of us will die when our Life hits 0?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sadistic Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey c'mon! What's wrong, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up and play a Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Jounouchi and I\N were being controlled by Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just when I things were\N getting sticky, you arrived at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind that I wanted\N my brother's face to be the first thing\N I saw when I took off my bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never would have {\i1}imagined{\i0}\N I'd see him like {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have time to grab my own key!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were separated, but now I'm by your side again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because your friends supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At last, I found you big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you went and jumped\N in the water all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we\N boarded the Battle Ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle Ship, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of the God Cards\N were gathered on board...\N the Three Illusionary Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time we witnessed the\N three cards being used was in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of the Aerial Duel Arena...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sacrifice Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Magnet Warrior Gamma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Big Shield Gardna, totaling three offerings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The advent of... Osiris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra's changing its form!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bring me victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awaken, Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show you God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come forth! Great War God Obelisk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting a bit chilly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my ultimate card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Bastard!\N -Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Android - Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Battle City Tournament\N has ended, everyone's started Dueling\N a lot more than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Kaiba Corporation has\N been advertising it more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they've started selling\N the Duel Disks at a low price!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I play two set cards\N face-down on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I think of Noah when I see\N all these kids Dueling like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah! You're really sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your knowledge may have advanced, but your heart has remained frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're still nothing but a child who knows nothing about the world or the people that inhabit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heh, I shouldn't have expected commoners like yourself to understand my greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm sure someone chosen by victory will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I've chosen {\b0}you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now all you have to do\N is say you'll serve me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using your power to try and sway people's hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do you expect people to accept you if you do things like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're acting really stupid, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After having lost his body,\N he was forced to live in Virtual Reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a lonely young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never had any friends\N to play with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Demon's Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on it now,\N I feel even sadder for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, let's put an end to all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to stay by my side forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}WHAT DO YOU\N THINK YOU'RE DOING, NOAH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}LET GO OF ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I STILL HAVE SOMETHING\N I NEED TO DO!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We died a long time ago, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}LET ME GO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I DON'T WANT TO DIE YET!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had met him\N in a different way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have liked\N to become friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost {\i1}again{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really strong, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm not gonna lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all Dueling like this\N and enjoying themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the Duels Yugi and the others\N fought weren't like this at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm headed to the Duel Ring\N where Kaiba's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you stay here and keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a {\b0}Duelist{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you guys to stay here\N with Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you saying Dueling is more\N important than Jounouchi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do you have to fight\N at a time like {\b0}this{\b1}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not just Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai-{\i0}san{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even that man named Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every one of them have fallen\N one after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've got nothing {\b0}left{\b1} to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fight because I\N promised Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Promised...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as people continue\N to search for answers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...they have a reason to live,\N a place to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm certain he'll return to us\N as his usual, energetic self!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}believe{\b1} in that future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We still have no idea what even\N happened to you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You still need to be properly tested!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said I'm {\b0}fine{\b1}, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's gun it, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The doctor's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to do what your\N medical overseer tells you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get what's goin' on in my body\N more than any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\b0}don't{\b1} know!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were practically {\b0}dead{\b1}\N just minutes ago, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've all been {\b0}worried sick{\b1} over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And here you are, making that face\N like nothing happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need to worry about your {\b0}body{\b1}\N before you start thinking about {\b0}Dueling{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have to go do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really am sorry\N for worrying you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Yugi's not the only one\N concerned about his battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to fight as well in order\N to keep my promise with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your... promise with him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Battle City isn't over until\N I settle things with Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both Yugi and me have been fighting\N in order to reach the point when we\N can call ourselves True Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter {\b0}who{\b1}\N it is we're Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're connected to each another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I want to watch how it ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to watch Yugi's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\b0}have{\b1} to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mutual feelings of trust and warmth\N between Yugi and Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friendship between men\N is really confusing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I feel like I've started to\N understand it a little better...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go to our next stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And after {\b0}finally{\b1} overcoming\N all of those hardships, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Battle City Finals are over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner is Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Yugi obtained all three\N God Cards at long last...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, here's the God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris the Heaven Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great War God Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the three God Cards\N are in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three cards hold the secret\N of the other me's memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The key to the Pharaoh's memories,\N which the Tomb Guardian clan\N has protected for centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It lies right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How awful that\N must have been...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's horrible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cruel scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is {\i1}this{\i0} how the Tomb Guardians\N guarded my memory for\N so many generations...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These hieroglyphs contain a prophecized\N message passed down from the first Tomb\N Guardian who served under the Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"In the future, one will come\N who will wield the power of the\N three gods depicted on the stone slab."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"This will be proof that the\N Pharaoh's soul has been reincarnated."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, since you now hold the three God Cards, it is proof that you are the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus, you deserve to know the\N {\b0}truth{\b1} of your long-lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That slate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my memory truly sealed\N within that slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's gathered all three\N of the God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the seal on his memories\N is lifted, the other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I realize I took up\N a lot of your time today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like there's something\N you're missing out on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had something\N {\i1}that important{\i0} planned!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "sort of" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have\N told me about this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know...\N I held you here with me for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah c'mon, it's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... In actuality,\N I only have a little time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pretty soon, the other Yugi's going to\N disappear right before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you visit\N Domino City frequently, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is... the proof of our friendship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother says this a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We're all connected with\N a bond of friendship," is what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bond of friendship...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've finally become\N friends with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were one of our friends\N a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, even if\N we're separated, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friends, even if we're separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not... have much more time\N to spend with the other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"We're friends, even if\N we're separated," huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I need to cherish the\N little time I have left with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the other Yugi begins the journey to find his lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, Haga and Ryuzaki are suddenly attacked by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And something strange happens when the three God Cards are faced towards the stone slab.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to add to the strangeness, Duel Monsters begin appearing all over the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Throbs of a New Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:23:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
